spec_data.Name: perl-Plack-Middleware-ForceEnv
spec_data.Description:
ForceEnv modifies the environment passed to the application by adding your
specified key value pairs. This is primarily useful when testing apps under
plackup (or similar) in a development environment.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 03:15:27 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Force set environment variables for testing
